data.message: Full design workout session: 3 refs, 9 variations, critique cycles: Travel Counsellors (85/90/92%), Design Trends (85-90/90-95/70-80%), Glassmorphism (82/84/86%). 14 learnings logged, 4 design refs stored, 2 strategic decisions on shipping/telemetry. Key insight: structure is solid, micro-execution (texture, depth, contrast zones) is the growth edge. Session established design workout as repeatable practice.
